quote.content: Keep your face to the sunshine and you cannot see the shadows.
The more you praise and celebrate your life, the more there is in life to celebrate. - Oprah Winfrey
Be happy for this moment. This moment is your life. ― Omar Khayyám
It's okay to cry, but don't forget to smile afterward.
This too shall pass away. ― Ella Wheeler Wilcox
Everything you've ever wanted is on the other side of fear. — George Addair
Anger is an acid that can do more harm to the vessel in which it is stored than to anything on which it is poured. — Mark Twain
What seems to us as bitter trials are often blessings in disguise.
The happiest people don't have the best of everything, they make the best of everything.
Sometimes the most scenic roads in life are the detours you didn't mean to take. - Angela N. Blount
Tears are words the heart can't express.
Smooth seas do not make good sailors -African Proverb
Necessity is the mother of invention and the father of crime
Ain't nothing behind you but some stuff you can't change
The wound is the place where the Light enters you. — Rumi
The most beautiful moments always seem to accelerate and slip beyond one's grasp just when you want to hold onto them for as long as possible. — E.A. Bucchianeri
Guilt is perhaps the most painful companion of death. — Coco Chanel
Character is how you treat those who can do nothing for you
Impossible is just a big word thrown around by small men who find it easier to live in the world they've been given than to explore the power they have to change it
Time is nature's way of keeping everything from happening at once.
I can accept failure, everyone fails at something. But I can't accept not trying. - Michael Jordan
